{"tid":436411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞裔社工:  有 Refugees係好事，顯示香港係一個 international city。","createTime":"2017-10-15T06:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T15:10:48.000Z","uid":82646,"like":5,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"024f6ba1911d3efe9a38ded4635169dca160643d","tid":436411,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1312/640pixfolder/N1312_078_KCM_150421_2651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1312%2F640pixfolder%2FN1312_078_KCM_150421_2651.jpg&h=a4f1aa31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJeff Andrews<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1312/640pixfolder/N1312_078_unnamed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1312%2F640pixfolder%2FN1312_078_unnamed.jpg&h=05425db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右三<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1312/640pixfolder/N1312_078_KCM_150421_2529cop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1312%2F640pixfolder%2FN1312_078_KCM_150421_2529cop.jpg&h=48de234a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在重慶大廈上班，處理難民個案。Jeffrey :「有 refugees係好事，顯示香港係一個 international city。佢哋唔會去中國或台灣。」</span>    <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(非常人語大都會)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.informationliberation.com/files/sadiq-khan-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.informationliberation.com%2Ffiles%2Fsadiq-khan-2.jpg&h=a771ccb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1312/640pixfolder/N1312_078_KCM_150425_3170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1312%2F640pixfolder%2FN1312_078_KCM_150425_3170.jpg&h=a5462c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Jeff看着難民的子女長大，細路見到他便蹦蹦跳跳走過來。他們在香港上學，廣東話和英文說得一樣好，還有中文名字。只是長得太快，去公園，本地小孩一下便被撞散。捐助基督教勵行會，可致電： 2716 8862。 </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">((非常人語大都會))</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　Jeffrey Andrews 小知識 <br />\n<br />\n- 2002年8月加入黑社會<br />\n<br />\n- 曾參與打鬥、收陀地、偷竊、召集人馬, 搶電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 2006年 打劫後被警察截查，人贓並獲<br />\n<br />\n- 融樂會前總幹事王惠芬協助保釋, 找來多封求情信<br />\n, 成功避過入獄及留案底, 只簽保守行為一年<br />\n<br />\n- 於基督教勵行會工作，負責輔導難民<br />\n<br />\n- 重慶大廈的服務中心工作<br />\n<br />\n- 2015, 成為社工<br />\n<br />\n- 2017, 南亞團體「Voices of Diversity」到政府總部外遞交請願信<br />\nJeff 指責本地幼稚園拒絕接收非本地學生，令他們缺乏學習中文的機會，導致 難以融入社會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Jeffery說: 他選擇繼續做難民服務。自己的角色一方面是協助難民，同時亦希望教育香港人<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMeanwhile in southern asia.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/http://www.radionz.co.nz/assets/news_crops/11240/eight_col_india.jpg?1464858022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.radionz.co.nz%2Fassets%2Fnews_crops%2F11240%2Feight_col_india.jpg%3F1464858022&h=adc06cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tvb4life.pixnet.net/blog/post/197352711-%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%9E-%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E3%80%80-jeffrey-andrews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftvb4life.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F197352711-%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%259E-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%2580-jeffrey-andrews&d=9SexdBNr%2F3onhzMWZ3wnKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a2afa9cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tvb4life.pixnet.net/blog/post/197352711-%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%9E-%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E3%80%80-jeffrey-andrews</a>"},{"pid":"dafb9e7687cbb1f0c71bd95aa93f8ca1ae5794f4","tid":436411,"uid":15696,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"- 曾參與打鬥、收陀地、偷竊、召集人馬, 搶電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 2006年 打劫後被警察截查，人贓並獲<br />\n<br />\n- 融樂會前總幹事王惠芬協助保釋, 找來多封求情信<br />\n, 成功避過入獄及留案底, 只簽保守行為一年"},{"pid":"3555922d8b7a75c247182102dbd0a218a2e62abd","tid":436411,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16e8fbe1457f0f3a1f9f1e130e9f29061b1752d","tid":436411,"uid":50533,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf5185c7fa02e292477f7ed7af32a922e8f48e69","tid":436411,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實上好多南亞人都好nice<br />\n香港人應該好好反省</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311a91c2f319141b0fa831be86b6e1f755939478","tid":436411,"uid":82646,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/http://i.dawn.com/large/2017/03/58c8e1dfdf0be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.dawn.com%2Flarge%2F2017%2F03%2F58c8e1dfdf0be.jpg&h=e66e6b01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3474b04c3a84e321787af66162a73f2a0a9263f6","tid":436411,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"FUCKING RETARDED<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61118a0d01357110e20d22c3813352bcfc5a8c53","tid":436411,"uid":15696,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>- 曾參與打鬥、收陀地、偷竊、召集人馬, 搶電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 2006年 打劫後被警察截查，人贓並獲<br />\n<br />\n- 融樂會前總幹事王惠芬協助保釋, 找來多封求情信<br />\n, 成